  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK382">
<l>añcāmai yīkai yaṟivūkka minnāṉkum</l>
<l>eñcāmai vēntaṟ kiyalpu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Never to fail in these four things, fearlessness, liberality, wisdom, and energy, is the kingly character.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
